title: Quilted Walnut Canister
description:
Occasionally you get a really nice piece of figured (quilted) hardwood.  That was the case with this particular vase I just finished.  I had been saving the piece of quilted Walnut for just the right occasion. 

This vase consists of 304 segments made from Walnut, Wenge, Maple and Padauk.  It is 10" in height and 9" in diameter.
